Add or Subtract Days or Months

In CRM Analytics, return the column date with the specified days or months added or removed.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
USER PERMISSIONS
NEEDED
To create a recipe:	Edit CRM Analytics Dataflows OR Edit Dataset Recipes

Add or Subtract Days or Months
Select one date column in the Preview tab.
Select the Formula button () in the Transform toolbar.
Select Add or Subtract Days or Months.
Configure the transformation.
Start Date Column is automatically filled with the date column you previously chose.

Choose Days or Months to add or subtract.
Select the number to add or subtract with the plus and minus buttons.
Choose the date format of the output column.
Optionally, change the label of the column that stores the result data in the Column Label field.
Click Apply to add the transformation to the Transform node.
title: Add or Subtract Days or Months in CRM Analytics
